Definition: leniency and compassion shown toward offenders by a person or agency charged with administering justice
Example: he threw himself on the mercy of the court
Synonyms: adj, all, clement, mercifulness, merciful, mercy, leniency, and, compassion, shown, toward, offenders, by, a, person, or, agency, charged, with, administering, justice, he, threw, himself, on, the, of, court
Category: noun.act
